<paragraph role="paragraph" id="par_id3146972" xml-lang="en-US" l10n="U" oldref="3">You can use <link href="text/simpress/main0209.xhp" name="rulers">rulers</link> to position objects in the workspace, to set paragraph indents or to drag <link href="text/simpress/01/04030000.xhp" name="guides">guides</link> onto the page.</paragraph>
